OL,3,CCoventry park cordoned off as body of
OL,4,Cman found in wheelie bin
OL,6,FPolice are investigating after a man
OL,7,Fwas found dead in a wheelie bin in
OL,8,FCoventry. His body was discovered in
OL,9,FCash's Park yesterday (March 13).
OL,11,FOfficers said the body of the man, who
OL,12,Fhas not yet been identified but who is
OL,13,Fbelieved to be aged 40 to 50, was
OL,14,Ffound in Cashs Park off Daimler Road
OL,15,Fat around 5 pm on Friday (March 13).
OL,17,FHe was found in a Coventry City
OL,18,FCouncil wheelie bin with a green lid.
OL,19,FPolice are working with the local
OL,20,Fauthority to identify the location of
OL,21,Fthe bin before it was moved.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/3
