OL,3,CCoventry park cordoned off as body of
OL,4,Cman found in wheelie bin
OL,6,FIt is believed he may have been hit by
OL,7,Fa vehicle before being moved to Cash's
OL,8,FPark. Police are carrying out urgent
OL,9,Fenquiries to establish who the man is
OL,10,Fand where and how he died.
OL,12,FOfficers remain at the scene today
OL,13,F(March 24) carrying out enquiries.
OL,14,FAnyone with information is urged to
OL,15,Fcontact West Midlands Police.
